 SecurityConfig extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter,

dwie metody:

1. configure
   - http.autorizeRequest().antMatchers("/user-only).hasRole("USER")
      - http.autorizeRequest().antMatchers("/admin-only).hasRole("ADMIN")
         - http.autorizeRequest().antMatchers("/everyone", "/**").permintAll()

2. userDetailsService
      User.UserBuilder users = User.withDefaultPasswordEncoder();
    InMemoryUserDetalisMenager menager =  new InMemoryUserDetalisMenager;
menager.createUser(users.username("admin").password("admin).roles("ADMIN", "USER")
